&quot;Dutch athletes walking round Amsterdam, in white skirts dark blazers and hats.&quot;

It looks like one of the canals (grachten). Maybe Prinsengracht? Look at the pavement and the cobbled roadway. I'm sure the modern cobbles are more rounded and rustic-looking.
Also note the gents' clothiers, Levie and Levit. A poignant note.
